title: How to Make Abstract Paintings (Technical).pdf
description:
How to Make Abstract Paintings
Viking Press | 1961 | English | 146 pages | PDF | 11 MB

This book explains techniques employed in creating abstract paintings similar to those currently being exhibited in galleries and museums. Few of the techniques employed by the representational painter are discussed, because the aims of the traditionalist and those of the abstract painter differ, and so do many of the materials they use
